des:
Want to know what your name would be if you were in Game of Thrones? Are you a Stark, Greyjoy or from Flea Bottom?
Simply ask Name of Thrones and we will tell you what your Game of Thrones character name would be and which house your fealty lies with.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
